content:
In addition to the Marketing Cloud activation target, you can now use rapid segment publish for activations to all hyperscaler targets, such as Amazon S3, SFTP, Google Cloud Storage, and Microsoft Azure Storage.

This change applies to Data Cloud in Developer, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions. 

This functionality is available starting in July 2024.

Create a Standard Segment
Increase Segment Refresh from Data Cloud to the Activation Targets
title: Rapidly Publishing Segments to Hyperscaler Targets
